If we can confirm
these hairs belong to the victim,

00:02:29.600 --> 00:02:32.720
then the owner of these clothes
is the real killer.

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:43.681
You're staying here all night,

00:02:43.681 --> 00:02:44.880
leaving your dad alone?

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:45.880
Ms. Wang's with him.

00:02:47.401 --> 00:02:48.521
Have you eaten?

00:02:49.160 --> 00:02:49.961
Bread's over there.

00:02:49.961 --> 00:02:50.760
Have some.

00:02:51.361 --> 00:02:52.841
Otherwise, your stomach will hurt.

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:56.720
I ate.

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:00.200
I'll go to Jiao.

00:03:18.801 --> 00:03:19.920
Any new clues?

00:03:20.281 --> 00:03:20.920
Master.

00:03:21.640 --> 00:03:22.081
Sit.

00:03:23.361 --> 00:03:25.160
Judging from this video,

00:03:25.160 --> 00:03:27.920
these two individuals have
very similar builds and clothing.

00:03:28.600 --> 00:03:30.241
The bag he's carrying

00:03:30.241 --> 00:03:33.681
is basically identical to the one
we fished out of the lake.

00:03:34.001 --> 00:03:36.640
So we can conclude
they're the same person.

00:03:38.681 --> 00:03:40.521
If they're the same person,

00:03:41.121 --> 00:03:45.121
then this person exited the south gate
of the community at 1:05 AM,

00:03:45.121 --> 00:03:47.681
and reached the pond by 1:15 AM.

00:03:48.001 --> 00:03:49.640
That's several kilometers away.

00:03:50.401 --> 00:03:51.361
He was quite quick.

00:03:51.600 --> 00:03:53.440
After dumping the bag,

00:03:53.640 --> 00:03:54.640
where did he go?

00:03:59.224 --> 00:04:03.960
(South gate, Pond)

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:05.801
Qian.

00:04:32.632 --> 00:04:35.736
(Yumo, long time no see)

00:04:44.056 --> 00:04:51.352
(Dan Qing, long time no see)

00:05:12.888 --> 00:05:14.776
(Dan Qing, long time no see.
Available this weekend?)

00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:19.481
He took the bait already?

00:05:19.921 --> 00:05:22.561
Seems he still can't forget you.

00:05:23.001 --> 00:05:23.640
Right?

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:28.960
Bao Hei will definitely
send people to watch.

00:05:29.361 --> 00:05:32.561
Let's hope your ex-boyfriend is smart.

00:05:33.801 --> 00:05:35.241
I don't care.

00:05:37.320 --> 00:05:38.921
As long as he takes the bait,

00:05:40.041 --> 00:05:41.241
he can't escape.

00:05:49.944 --> 00:05:51.400
(Yunxi Police Department)

00:05:51.400 --> 00:05:52.721
The blood

00:05:52.921 --> 00:05:54.921
(Hauled up: Sports jacket, scalpel, etc.)
on the gloves and on the scalpel

00:05:54.921 --> 00:05:57.520
are confirmed to belong
to the victim, Wang Xiaole.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:00.520
On the sports jacket,

00:06:00.520 --> 00:06:02.760
I detected two different DNAs.

00:06:02.760 --> 00:06:04.840
One belongs to the victim Wang Xiaole,

00:06:04.840 --> 00:06:07.561
the other is from an unknown male.

00:06:08.121 --> 00:06:11.921
I found some hairs
on the zipper of the sports jacket.

00:06:11.921 --> 00:06:14.721
Testing confirmed they also
belong to the victim Wang Xiaole.

00:06:14.840 --> 00:06:16.400
Based on the location, I speculate

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:17.440
when the killer

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:18.840
(Hauled up: Key, rubber gloves, etc.)
grabbed Wang Xiaole's hair,

00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:21.001
he tore it out during repeated impacts.

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:25.681
So we can be fairly certain
this unknown male is the killer.

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:28.681
Can we find this person using the DNA?

00:06:29.161 --> 00:06:30.880
I've already uploaded the data.

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:33.520
If this person has a previous record
in our system,

00:06:33.520 --> 00:06:34.760
then we'll find him quickly.

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:36.161
But if not,

00:06:36.320 --> 00:06:39.200
then I can only run a comparison
after we apprehend a suspect.

00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:43.080
But we can confirm it's not Wu Da.

00:06:43.481 --> 00:06:46.320
This key appears to be a duplicate.

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:49.041
Does it open
the victim's apartment door?

00:06:49.200 --> 00:06:50.280
We've tried, Captain Leng.

00:06:50.280 --> 00:06:50.960
It does open.

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:53.760
That bag looks like the giveaway
for signing up for a gym membership.

00:06:53.921 --> 00:06:55.481
If there's a brand on the bag,

00:06:55.481 --> 00:06:56.960
we could trace it.

00:06:57.161 --> 00:06:59.561
That gym went out of business years ago.

00:07:07.880 --> 00:07:09.921
Long, go sleep in my room.

00:07:11.721 --> 00:07:14.320
No prints on that thing.

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:16.041
He wore gloves.

00:07:17.161 --> 00:07:19.721
Young people can sleep soundly.
I really envy him.

00:07:20.640 --> 00:07:23.880
I have some findings on the video.

00:07:26.104 --> 00:07:28.152
(Dongyuan, Alley 07)

00:07:28.152 --> 00:07:30.808
But it can't be enlarged any further.
This is the best it gets.

00:07:31.064 --> 00:07:35.161
Now we know the person is
in medium build, on the thin side.

00:07:36.080 --> 00:07:39.041
Estimated height
between 1.75m and 1.80m.

00:07:40.361 --> 00:07:42.280
He was heading towards Dongyuan.

00:07:43.121 --> 00:07:44.880
Dongyuan is an urban village.

00:07:45.481 --> 00:07:48.001
The permanent population
might be at least 3,000.

00:07:48.001 --> 00:07:48.640
Oh, no.

00:07:48.921 --> 00:07:50.361
That's just permanent population.

00:07:50.520 --> 00:07:52.481
Including migrant population,
it would be more.

00:07:52.481 --> 00:07:53.320
That's much more.

00:07:53.921 --> 00:07:56.921
The roads and terrain
in Dongyuan are complex.

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:02.080
There are only about
seven or eight cameras total.

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:03.520
Too many blind spots.

00:08:04.601 --> 00:08:06.921
If he is a resident of Dongyuan,
that would be manageable.

00:08:07.400 --> 00:08:08.440
If he just passed through

00:08:08.440 --> 00:08:12.681
Dongyuan or hid there
briefly before leaving,

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:14.001
that makes it tricky.

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:17.121
I'll say something.

00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:20.440
We currently know the suspect

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:23.128
had been peeking at the victim
for years from the pine woods

00:08:23.128 --> 00:08:24.208
behind Shancheng Community.

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:26.921
That shows he's quite familiar
with the surrounding terrain.

00:08:27.400 --> 00:08:29.280
West of Shancheng Community,

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:30.561
less than 500 meters away

00:08:30.561 --> 00:08:31.840
(Map)
is the Ring Road.

00:08:32.040 --> 00:08:33.880
The traffic there is very convenient.

00:08:33.961 --> 00:08:35.961
He could discard the clothes
along the way.

00:08:35.961 --> 00:08:38.104
The suspect left Shancheng Community

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:39.880
after the crime
without drawing attention.

00:08:40.001 --> 00:08:43.520
So I don't think he would
deliberately take a detour

00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:45.481
to Dongyuan in the opposite direction.

00:08:45.640 --> 00:08:48.400
That'd also increase the risk
of being spotted and noticed.

00:08:55.241 --> 00:08:58.920
I think even if the suspect isn't
a permanent resident of Dongyuan,

00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:00.800
he at least frequents this area.

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:05.481
Captain Leng, I think

00:09:05.721 --> 00:09:08.481
if we take action
in the Dongyuan jurisdiction now,

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:11.760
we might alert the suspect
and he might flee?

00:09:13.361 --> 00:09:16.640
Our operation to dredge the sewage pond
was quite a scene.

00:09:17.441 --> 00:09:20.560
If the suspect was watching
from the shadows,

00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:24.241
he must have alerted by now.

00:09:26.121 --> 00:09:28.520
Otherwise, to be safe,

00:09:28.520 --> 00:09:31.576
we'll first coordinate with
the community security unit,

00:09:31.576 --> 00:09:34.400
and conduct a sweep under the pretext
of preventing robbery and theft.

00:09:34.400 --> 00:09:36.880
Start with the permanent residents.

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:38.560
You, Wang Tong.

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:39.121
Here!

00:09:39.121 --> 00:09:39.680
Liu Yang.

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:40.081
Here!

00:09:40.081 --> 00:09:42.296
Based on the social circles
of Wu Da and Wang Xiaole,

00:09:42.991 --> 00:09:44.241
you conduct an investigation

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:47.280
to see if anyone has connections
to the Dongyuan area.

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:48.280
Action! Hurry!

00:09:48.280 --> 00:09:48.760
- Yes!
- Yes!

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:04.920
This is the Dongyuan urban village.

00:10:04.920 --> 00:10:06.241
Let's go take a look.

00:10:07.081 --> 00:10:07.760
Alright.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:08.201
This way.

00:10:16.201 --> 00:10:17.040
Who's the owner?

00:10:17.201 --> 00:10:18.800
Me! I'm the owner.

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:20.201
Ask you something.

00:10:20.400 --> 00:10:21.361
We're from CID.

00:10:21.361 --> 00:10:21.880
Okay.

00:10:25.841 --> 00:10:26.481
Ma'am.

00:10:26.880 --> 00:10:27.560
Yes?

00:10:27.560 --> 00:10:28.280
Ask you something.

00:10:28.520 --> 00:10:29.361
What is it?

00:10:29.640 --> 00:10:32.201
Are your customers all regulars?

00:10:32.361 --> 00:10:33.640
- Any unfamiliar faces?
- Yes.

00:10:33.640 --> 00:10:35.361
All residents from nearby.

00:10:35.361 --> 00:10:36.121
All residents?

00:10:36.400 --> 00:10:36.760
Yes.

00:10:36.760 --> 00:10:37.520
No strangers?

00:10:37.601 --> 00:10:38.121
No.

00:10:39.280 --> 00:10:40.081
Just ahead.

00:10:41.361 --> 00:10:42.121
Thank you.

00:10:42.280 --> 00:10:43.081
Okay, no problem.

00:10:51.081 --> 00:10:51.880
This one's ready.

00:10:52.201 --> 00:10:52.640
Hurry.

00:10:55.520 --> 00:10:56.361
Okay. Come on.

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:58.441
Have one.

00:10:59.560 --> 00:11:00.241
I'm not hungry.

00:11:03.121 --> 00:11:04.040
Take it easy.

00:11:05.720 --> 00:11:07.224
How long have you been a policeman?

00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:09.241
Four years.

00:11:10.081 --> 00:11:10.880
Four years?

00:11:13.841 --> 00:11:14.401
Well, I...

00:11:15.192 --> 00:11:16.920
I became a policeman at twenty.

00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:19.441
I'll be retiring soon.

00:11:19.520 --> 00:11:23.400
I wanted to go all out
on this Shancheng case.

00:11:24.201 --> 00:11:26.721
But I'm old now, not capable as before.

00:11:27.040 --> 00:11:28.841
Can't keep up
with you young folks anymore.

00:11:37.560 --> 00:11:38.520
What flavor?

00:11:56.560 --> 00:11:57.160
Ms. Wang.

00:11:57.920 --> 00:11:58.680
You're back.

00:11:59.081 --> 00:12:00.481
Dinner's kept warm for you.

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:02.721
Go wash your hands and eat.

00:12:03.241 --> 00:12:04.040
Dad.

00:12:14.441 --> 00:12:15.441
Leng.

00:12:15.721 --> 00:12:18.280
I won't wash these dishes
of yours today, okay?

00:12:18.520 --> 00:12:20.361
Well, you got off work early.

00:12:20.361 --> 00:12:22.441
I want to go back early today.

00:12:22.640 --> 00:12:25.201
My daughter brought the kids over

00:12:25.201 --> 00:12:27.361
and they're staying
at my place for a few days.

00:12:27.800 --> 00:12:29.520
Alright. Thank you.

00:12:30.880 --> 00:12:33.321
Leng, well...

00:12:34.040 --> 00:12:36.920
I've worked for you
for years now, right?

00:12:37.081 --> 00:12:39.680
Well, we know each other pretty well.

00:12:41.280 --> 00:12:44.640
You know how expensive
everything is nowadays.

00:12:45.400 --> 00:12:48.201
I have elderly and kids to support.

00:12:48.312 --> 00:12:49.321
- I need to...
- Ms. Wang.

00:12:49.520 --> 00:12:50.441
Ms. Wang, I understand.

00:12:50.640 --> 00:12:53.040
My dad can't be left alone.

00:12:53.280 --> 00:12:56.680
Well, I'll give you
an extra 800 yuan a month.

00:12:56.680 --> 00:12:57.680
What do you think?

00:12:59.201 --> 00:13:01.241
That's too much.

00:13:02.001 --> 00:13:02.800
Thank you.

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:05.121
My job is really demanding.

00:13:05.800 --> 00:13:07.160
You really helped me a lot.

00:13:07.841 --> 00:13:08.601
No problem.

00:13:08.760 --> 00:13:09.841
Then it's settled.

00:13:09.841 --> 00:13:10.441
Okay.

00:13:10.640 --> 00:13:11.601
I-I'm leaving then.

00:13:11.601 --> 00:13:12.721
Alright. Take care.

00:13:54.601 --> 00:13:56.081
I saw it online.

00:13:56.601 --> 00:13:59.241
Didn't expect
he's running an art gallery now.

00:14:26.008 --> 00:14:33.624
(Phone password)

00:15:07.280 --> 00:15:09.121
Okay, see you then.

00:15:10.121 --> 00:15:10.920
Who's it?

00:15:11.721 --> 00:15:12.961
Who are you meeting then?

00:15:13.361 --> 00:15:14.361
None of your business.

00:15:14.841 --> 00:15:16.160
Is it your unrequited love?

00:15:16.920 --> 00:15:18.601
How's it going? Tell me.

00:15:23.400 --> 00:15:24.800
You're wearing this tomorrow?

00:15:28.441 --> 00:15:29.001
What's wrong?

00:15:30.601 --> 00:15:32.961
It's nice. Suits you.

00:15:39.081 --> 00:15:39.880
Good taste.

00:15:57.040 --> 00:15:57.760
Master.

00:15:58.841 --> 00:16:00.361
New info from the medical school.

00:16:00.560 --> 00:16:03.201
They found the guy who got into
a fight with Wu Da during school.

00:16:04.481 --> 00:16:05.800
He is Niu Bosheng,

00:16:05.961 --> 00:16:07.321
male, 34 years old,

00:16:07.321 --> 00:16:08.001
a local.

00:16:08.560 --> 00:16:10.841
Ph.D. in Clinical Medicine
from Yunxi Medical University.

00:16:11.841 --> 00:16:14.760
They were in the same year at college,
but in different classes.

00:16:15.280 --> 00:16:18.241
He attended the same middle school
and high school as Wang Xiaole.

00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:21.280
He joined the mountaineering club
in college.

00:16:21.432 --> 00:16:24.152
After graduation, he worked
in General Surgery at Central Hospital.

00:16:24.952 --> 00:16:26.441
Under the counterpart support policy,

00:16:26.441 --> 00:16:30.201
he holds clinic hours every Wednesday
at Dongyuan Community Health Center.

00:16:31.321 --> 00:16:33.640
Wu Da got into a physical fight
with him during school.

00:16:33.880 --> 00:16:35.081
They got a demerit for it.

00:16:35.880 --> 00:16:37.721
So why did they fight?

00:16:38.560 --> 00:16:41.841
Wu Da accused Niu Bosheng
of peeking and harassing Wang Xiaole.

00:16:48.248 --> 00:16:56.472
(Yunxi Central Hospital)

00:16:57.400 --> 00:16:58.400
You did it on purpose?

00:16:59.441 --> 00:17:01.040
Didn't we agree not to wear it together?

00:17:01.481 --> 00:17:03.001
I swear on my life, man.

00:17:03.001 --> 00:17:04.360
I was sleeping when you got up.

00:17:04.360 --> 00:17:05.881
How did I know you'd wear this?

00:17:07.001 --> 00:17:07.961
If you can't stand it,

00:17:07.961 --> 00:17:09.520
there's a clothing store.

00:17:09.520 --> 00:17:10.481
Go buy a new one.

00:17:11.560 --> 00:17:12.560
Why don't you buy one?

00:17:12.760 --> 00:17:14.040
First, this isn't my fault.

00:17:14.040 --> 00:17:15.441
You should've told me last night.

00:17:15.441 --> 00:17:17.320
Second, I'm broke.

00:17:23.481 --> 00:17:25.080
It's field work today.

00:17:25.441 --> 00:17:26.520
Why are you coming along?

00:17:26.760 --> 00:17:27.641
Your master said

00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:30.280
that person is basically
a high-IQ criminal.

00:17:30.280 --> 00:17:31.721
You might need help, so he sent me.

00:17:34.320 --> 00:17:37.320
Don't reveal who we are at first.
Just talk to him.

00:17:37.641 --> 00:17:38.560
See how he reacts.

00:17:39.001 --> 00:17:40.360
Of course. Let's go.

00:17:44.441 --> 00:17:45.560
That's it?

00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:47.641
Yes. Enter the info and hit submit.

00:17:47.760 --> 00:17:48.600
That's it.

00:17:48.600 --> 00:17:49.481
Okay, thanks.

00:17:49.481 --> 00:17:49.961
No problem.

00:17:52.401 --> 00:17:53.201
Registered.

00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:03.161
You! Stay away from me!

00:18:04.881 --> 00:18:06.681
Where can I go? It's crowded here.

00:18:06.961 --> 00:18:08.201
I wish to stay away from you.

00:18:16.481 --> 00:18:18.201
Way too crowded.

00:18:19.080 --> 00:18:22.560
All hospitals are like this, crowded.

00:18:23.961 --> 00:18:24.800
Definitely.

00:18:26.001 --> 00:18:30.080
(Patient 047, Si Yuanlong,
please proceed to Room 1.)

00:18:31.241 --> 00:18:32.201
Let's go.

00:18:37.881 --> 00:18:39.201
Which one of you is the patient?

00:18:41.481 --> 00:18:43.641
Me. He's just here with me.

00:18:45.201 --> 00:18:47.241
A grown man needs company
to see the doctor?

00:18:47.641 --> 00:18:49.520
I'm emotionally fragile.

00:18:49.681 --> 00:18:50.600
What's the problem?

00:18:53.201 --> 00:18:54.120
My hand hurts.

00:18:57.681 --> 00:18:59.001
The wound's healing okay.

00:18:59.721 --> 00:19:02.080
Scar tissue doesn't look hypertrophic.

00:19:02.600 --> 00:19:03.641
How did this happen?

00:19:05.040 --> 00:19:06.008
Well...

00:19:07.352 --> 00:19:07.921
It...

00:19:09.280 --> 00:19:11.201
He got drunk and rowdy with me.

00:19:11.201 --> 00:19:12.201
He even pulled a knife

00:19:12.201 --> 00:19:13.520
and said I stole his girlfriend.

00:19:13.520 --> 00:19:14.641
Tell me, is he crazy?

00:19:15.161 --> 00:19:15.760
Listen up!

00:19:15.760 --> 00:19:17.201
I want all of it covered,

00:19:17.201 --> 00:19:19.080
the medical bills,
the trauma, everything!

00:19:19.401 --> 00:19:21.401
Why should I pay? Not a chance!

00:19:21.721 --> 00:19:23.681
You kept texting my girlfriend,

00:19:23.681 --> 00:19:25.520
like a ghost haunting me.

00:19:25.520 --> 00:19:27.080
Yet you want me to pay your bills?

00:19:27.080 --> 00:19:27.881
Wanting a beating?

00:19:28.520 --> 00:19:30.481
Me? You're insane!

00:19:31.040 --> 00:19:31.961
You always pester her.

00:19:31.961 --> 00:19:33.961
It's one-sided love. You know?

00:19:33.961 --> 00:19:35.360
Your girlfriend? You...

00:19:35.360 --> 00:19:35.960
You...

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:40.881
You two, go out if you want to quarrel.

00:19:40.881 --> 00:19:41.721
This is a hospital.

00:19:44.641 --> 00:19:46.881
I'll prescribe you
erythromycin ointment.

00:19:46.881 --> 00:19:48.120
Apply it for several days.

00:19:49.881 --> 00:19:50.641
Okay.

00:19:50.641 --> 00:19:51.241
Alright.

00:19:52.600 --> 00:19:53.600
Anything else?

00:19:57.600 --> 00:19:58.320
What's going on?

00:19:58.641 --> 00:19:59.600
Sorry, Doctor.

00:20:07.201 --> 00:20:07.881
Sorry.

