00:24:21.401 --> 00:24:23.201
It's real, not a joke.

00:24:23.401 --> 00:24:24.881
Do you still want to be my friend?

00:24:26.441 --> 00:24:28.201
I really enjoy being friends with you.

00:24:28.401 --> 00:24:30.120
But I don't like you as my boyfriend.

00:24:32.641 --> 00:24:33.481
And you, Ye Qian.

00:24:33.481 --> 00:24:35.080
