00:25:30.201 --> 00:25:31.040
Don't mind it.

00:25:31.320 --> 00:25:32.721
It's fine.

00:25:32.721 --> 00:25:33.800
I'm glad that you see me

00:25:33.800 --> 00:25:35.320
as a friend. Really.

00:25:35.441 --> 00:25:37.280
And I don't have many merits,

00:25:37.401 --> 00:25:39.201
but I'm definitely thick-skinned.

00:25:43.080 --> 00:25:45.001
Did he get any news
about Chen Yumo recently?

00:25:50.641 --> 00:25:52.280
