00:26:04.641 --> 00:26:06.921
Probably with his unrequited love.

00:26:07.280 --> 00:26:09.241
But I don't know the details.

00:26:09.241 --> 00:26:11.721
I just overheard them
chatting on WeChat.

00:26:11.721 --> 00:26:13.120
Do you know where they're going?

00:26:13.641 --> 00:26:15.641
