is anything but easy.

00:29:00.280 --> 00:29:01.320
It's really exhausting,

00:29:01.800 --> 00:29:03.560
with no fixed holidays

00:29:04.401 --> 00:29:05.201
or high pay.

00:29:05.401 --> 00:29:06.481
Just look how broke I am.

00:29:08.441 --> 00:29:10.800
But later, I thought it over.

00:29:11.921 --> 00:29:14.424
Becoming a policeman
is absolutely the best choice

00:29:14.424 --> 00:29:16.312
I've made in over 20 years.

00:29:17.441 --> 00:29:19.800
The sense of achievement

00:29:19.800 --> 00:29:22.881
from cracking a case

00:29:23.001 --> 00:29:24.721
with some clues

00:29:25.800 --> 00:29:29.641
is something no amount
of money can ever buy.

00:29:43.201 --> 00:29:44.191
Get him to talk about

00:29:44.191 --> 00:29:46.800
that fight with Wu Da
in med school that got him demerits.

00:29:50.320 --> 00:29:51.001
Talk.

