He even suspected
I had an affair with Xiaole.

00:30:01.360 --> 00:30:02.921
Then we got into a fight.

00:30:03.921 --> 00:30:06.800
But at least that day,

00:30:07.040 --> 00:30:09.520
Xiaole finally knew about me.

00:30:10.800 --> 00:30:15.120
Honestly, I never meant
to disrupt their lives.

00:30:15.921 --> 00:30:18.320
I just wanted to watch over her quietly.

00:30:19.641 --> 00:30:23.320
At first, Wu Da seemed like
a decent boyfriend.

00:30:24.320 --> 00:30:25.641
He treated Xiaole well,

00:30:26.320 --> 00:30:27.441
and seemed faithful.

00:30:30.120 --> 00:30:31.961
But he just couldn't make it big.

00:30:32.560 --> 00:30:34.600
He couldn't even hold a scalpel steady,

00:30:35.001 --> 00:30:36.520
so he couldn't become a doctor.

00:30:37.840 --> 00:30:41.320
Seeing all those pharmaceutical reps
making big money,

00:30:41.921 --> 00:30:43.641
he can barely scrape by.

00:30:44.800 --> 00:30:46.600
But poor Xiaole suffered,

00:30:48.001 --> 00:30:49.600
living in such a remote place.

00:30:51.520 --> 00:30:56.560
Actually, he didn't buy
that second-hand apartment himself.

