Besides,

00:31:29.320 --> 00:31:31.360
he even needs to borrow money

00:31:31.600 --> 00:31:34.001
to buy that second-hand apartment
in Shancheng Community.

00:31:34.001 --> 00:31:35.560
He's really hit rock bottom.

00:31:35.961 --> 00:31:37.840
He asked me
and I didn't know what to do.

00:31:37.840 --> 00:31:38.481
You know?

00:31:39.280 --> 00:31:40.080
Don't lend him.

