00:32:07.481 --> 00:32:09.201
Actually, we didn't even greet.

00:32:10.280 --> 00:32:11.360
But I loved Xiaole.

00:32:12.080 --> 00:32:14.280
I can't stand seeing
Xiaole suffer like this.

00:32:14.921 --> 00:32:16.681
I took out 200,000 yuan myself.

00:32:17.320 --> 00:32:20.800
I got a classmate to lend it
to Wu Da in his name.

00:32:21.201 --> 00:32:22.161
Then what?

00:32:22.881 --> 00:32:24.984
You asked the hospital leadership

00:32:25.688 --> 00:32:30.080
to take on the task at the Dongyuan
Community Health Center, right?

00:32:30.681 --> 00:32:34.001
Just to get closer
to Wang Xiaole, right?

00:32:35.721 --> 00:32:36.520
Right?

00:32:39.120 --> 00:32:39.921
Right.

00:32:40.881 --> 00:32:42.760
I didn't want to be too far from Xiaole.

00:32:44.001 --> 00:32:45.401
I don't trust Wu Da.

