Don't trust him?

00:32:50.280 --> 00:32:52.600
So you went to peek at her

00:32:53.481 --> 00:32:56.001
and did that disgusting thing
up in a tree?

00:35:20.680 --> 00:35:21.761
I love Xiaole.

