Right? I have desires too.

00:35:35.801 --> 00:35:37.600
Like Nabokov said,

00:35:38.801 --> 00:35:40.560
Xiaole is my life's light,

00:35:41.680 --> 00:35:42.680
my desire's fire.

00:35:43.961 --> 00:35:45.080
She is my goddess,

00:35:45.961 --> 00:35:46.961
my soul,

00:35:49.401 --> 00:35:50.560
and also my sin.

