Because I truly love her.

00:36:04.761 --> 00:36:07.361
Xiaole was shining to me,

00:36:08.160 --> 00:36:10.720
making everything else in the world dim.

00:36:11.680 --> 00:36:12.801
All I can do is,

00:36:14.720 --> 00:36:15.401
silently,

00:36:16.281 --> 00:36:17.080
secretly,

00:36:18.200 --> 00:36:22.680
far away in a corner, to watch over her,

00:36:23.560 --> 00:36:24.401
bless her,

00:36:25.441 --> 00:36:26.240
and love her.

00:36:53.080 --> 00:36:54.881
It's been so long.

