I'll do whatever you say.

00:37:28.761 --> 00:37:29.401
Deal.

00:37:29.801 --> 00:37:30.481
Deal.

00:37:30.481 --> 00:37:31.200
Deal.

00:37:45.600 --> 00:37:46.520
Ye Qian.

