On the night of the crime,

00:39:28.801 --> 00:39:32.040
what were you doing
between 12 AM to 1 AM?

00:39:33.080 --> 00:39:34.001
Sleeping at home.

00:39:34.160 --> 00:39:35.120
With whom?

00:39:36.361 --> 00:39:37.160
By myself.

00:39:38.120 --> 00:39:39.120
Where do you live?

00:39:40.080 --> 00:39:40.881
Guanlan Court.

