I did own an identical jacket
and the same bag.

00:40:38.560 --> 00:40:40.080
But both items were stolen.

00:40:40.281 --> 00:40:41.040
Stolen?

00:40:41.720 --> 00:40:42.720
Where were they stolen?

00:40:43.321 --> 00:40:44.120
Six months ago,

00:40:45.001 --> 00:40:48.040
I kept that jacket as a spare

00:40:48.720 --> 00:40:51.520
in the locker room
at the Dongyuan Community.

00:40:51.761 --> 00:40:53.321
But my locker was pried open

00:40:53.560 --> 00:40:54.921
and I couldn't find them.

00:40:55.560 --> 00:40:57.120
Some colleagues and the security guards

00:40:57.120 --> 00:40:58.200
can prove this.

00:40:58.680 --> 00:41:01.881
Since the stolen items weren't valuable,
I didn't report it to the police.

00:41:12.720 --> 00:41:14.040
Here. Qingbuliang.

00:41:15.441 --> 00:41:17.441
I heard their qingbuliang is delicious.

00:41:18.001 --> 00:41:18.640
Try some.

00:41:19.761 --> 00:41:21.040
Not in the mood.

00:41:35.441 --> 00:41:36.841
What kind of art exhibition?

00:41:36.841 --> 00:41:38.240
It takes that long?

00:41:42.001 --> 00:41:42.881
In my opinion,

00:41:43.120 --> 00:41:47.600
Little Qian finally
got to see his unrequited love.

00:41:48.080 --> 00:41:50.281
He must have
a lot of things to talk about

00:41:50.281 --> 00:41:51.160
and memories to share.

00:41:51.160 --> 00:41:54.001
He must cherish
every single moment with her.

00:42:01.160 --> 00:42:03.281
Hey, where are you going?
The night snack is on me.

00:42:05.281 --> 00:42:07.361
Wait, I came straight
after work to be with you.

